    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >▲ 简介</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《墨缇斯：霾影季度》是一款包含了模拟经营玩法的软科幻题材视觉小说游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个后冷战的世界里，你将扮演墨缇斯生物研习所的外勤部研习官，通过一次次的观测旅行，见证往日潮流中的人事变迁，寻找涨落的起源和真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137670/extras/d8b742f523378101d706c747a2e89a48.avif?t=1772273693\" width=1280 height=720 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137670/extras/89f9a04a9e305eb2077eb8c8ca391526.avif?t=1772273693\" width=1280 height=720 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>▲ 观测探索</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一次次的观测中，穿梭于不同时间的各个场景，见证往日潮流中的人事变迁。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137670/extras/37c60f957b8f8920e28a6b5d465528f5.avif?t=1772273693\" width=1280 height=720 /></span><br>▲ 介质收集 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过探索获得不同特性的涨落能介质，合成各种涨落工业设备，为接下来的观测提供助力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137670/extras/30898bcbcc0111c320a81f87ce4ff9ae.avif?t=1772273693\" width=1280 height=720 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >▲ 涨落监测</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >监测世界各地的涨落指标和工业设备情况，应对随时可能到来的涨落风暴。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137670/extras/8d5b32af53a64c43690e91e8cb3ecb6a.avif?t=1772273693\" width=1280 height=720 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137670/extras/ff33757d9ce7ade4a3ab5f8c0df560d3.avif?t=1772273693\" width=1280 height=720 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >▲ 模拟经营</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过月岚山交易中心，管理和交易各式各样的介质与商品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137670/extras/f8ba9d963500231dfdb406768a9a0a92.avif?t=1772273693\" width=1280 height=720 /></span></p>",
